<br>
As a result most people, regardless if they are die hard levelers or just casual players, tend to be in the 50+ range.  There are very few people who are truely new to the game anymore.  However, feel free to ask your questions, even if you think they are &quot;beneath&quot; asking.  <br>
<br>
Look at the responce to Dracca.  Most people enjoy and happily recant thier time in lower levels and lower zones adventuring and are more often than not happy to lend a hand should they be on the same server. <p><hr>
